body:
Low Pri ask.

Add a way for us blur child views and such.  Specifically useful when like a modal pops up or something and you want to blur all the child elements. 


Here is how we currently handle it on Android Java. With a custom View by eightbitlab

```

import eightbitlab.com.blurview.BlurView;
import eightbitlab.com.blurview.RenderScriptBlur;

public class CustomBlurView extends BlurView{
... setBlurRadius  25.0f
}
...
public class CustomBlurViewManager extends ViewGroupManager<CustomBlurView> {

}
```
